02928/2022-Santa-Cruz-Bronson-geometry-mullet-1-800x390.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07102928/2022-Santa-Cruz-Bronson-geometry-mullet-1-120x59.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07102928/2022-Santa-Cruz-Bronson-geometry-mullet-1-768x374.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07102928/2022-Santa-Cruz-Bronson-geometry-mullet-1-696x339.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07102928/2022-Santa-Cruz-Bronson-geometry-mullet-1-1068x521.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07102928/2022-Santa-Cruz-Bronson-geometry-mullet-1-862x420.jpg 862w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07102928/2022-Santa-Cruz-Bronson-geometry-mullet-1-533x261.jpg 533w\"></a>Why would you buy the Roubion over the Bronson?</h3><p>Despite the fact that the 2022 Juliana Roubion and Santa Cruz Bronson frames are identical, there are some factors that might sway your decision one way or the other. Beyond the difference in colorways, that is.</p><figure id=\"attachment_261156\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-261156\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07090433/2022-santa-cruz-bronson.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07090433/2022-santa-cruz-bronson.jpg\" alt=\"2022 santa cruz bronson vero sandler\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07090433/2022-santa-cruz-bronson.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07090433/2022-santa-cruz-bronson-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07090433/2022-santa-cruz-bronson-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07090433/2022-santa-cruz-bronson-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07090433/2022-santa-cruz-bronson-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07090433/2022-santa-cruz-bronson-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07090433/2022-santa-cruz-bronson-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07090433/2022-santa-cruz-bronson-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb13 src ng ngcb13 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07090433/2022-santa-cruz-bronson.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07090433/2022-santa-cruz-bronson.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07090433/2022-santa-cruz-bronson-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07090433/2022-santa-cruz-bronson-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07090433/2022-santa-cruz-bronson-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07090433/2022-santa-cruz-bronson-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07090433/2022-santa-cruz-bronson-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07090433/2022-santa-cruz-bronson-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07090433/2022-santa-cruz-bronson-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-261156\">Veronique Sandler riding the <a href=\"https://wp.me/pcUhB6-15V6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">2022 Santa Cruz Bronson</a></figcaption></figure><p>The Roubion gets a slightly different shock tune, setup with a lighter compression and rebound damping tune said to work better for lighter riders. That said, freerider Veronique Sandler rides a Santa Cruz with the heavier shock tune (granted, we aren’t all riding the Vision Line at warp speed, or back flipping to dirt).&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07102533/2022-juliana-roubion-mullet-mtb.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07102533/2022-juliana-roubion-mullet-mtb.jpg\" alt=\"juliana roubion\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07102533/2022-juliana-roubion-mullet-mtb.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07102533/2022-juliana-roubion-mullet-mtb-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07102533/2022-juliana-roubion-mullet-mtb-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07102533/2022-juliana-roubion-mullet-mtb-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07102533/2022-juliana-roubion-mullet-mtb-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07102533/2022-juliana-roubion-mullet-mtb-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07102533/2022-juliana-roubion-mullet-mtb-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07102533/2022-juliana-roubion-mullet-mtb-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb13 src ng ngcb13 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07102533/2022-juliana-roubion-mullet-mtb.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07102533/2022-juliana-roubion-mullet-mtb.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07102533/2022-juliana-roubion-mullet-mtb-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07102533/2022-juliana-roubion-mullet-mtb-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07102533/2022-juliana-roubion-mullet-mtb-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07102533/2022-juliana-roubion-mullet-mtb-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07102533/2022-juliana-roubion-mullet-mtb-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07102533/2022-juliana-roubion-mullet-mtb-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07102533/2022-juliana-roubion-mullet-mtb-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>Other considerations would be the contact points, of course. The Roubion gets a women’s specific saddle in the form of the Juliana Segundo (though, you can switch it out for the WTB Volt if you prefer that). It also gets the 30mm Juliana House grip, which can also be swapped for Greg Minnaar’s Burgtec Bartender Pro.</p><h3>Pricing &amp; Availability</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07102620/2022-juliana-roubion-mullet-mtb-steep-rock-slab.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07102620/2022-juliana-roubion-mullet-mtb-steep-rock-slab.jpg\" alt=\"2022 juliana roubion\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07102620/2022-juliana-roubion-mullet-mtb-steep-rock-slab.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07102620/2022-juliana-roubion-mullet-mtb-steep-rock-slab-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07102620/2022-juliana-roubion-mullet-mtb-steep-rock-slab-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07102620/2022-juliana-roubion-mullet-mtb-steep-rock-slab-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07102620/2022-juliana-roubion-mullet-mtb-steep-rock-slab-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07102620/2022-juliana-roubion-mullet-mtb-steep-rock-slab-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07102620/2022-juliana-roubion-mullet-mtb-steep-rock-slab-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07102620/2022-juliana-roubion-mullet-mtb-steep-rock-slab-630x420.jpg 630w\" size